      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "INDIANAPOLIS, Indr., Jan. 49,\nThe miners federation convention\nthis morning adopted resolution\ncriticizing the governors of Colora-\ndo and Idaho for what they termed\nthe unwarranted prosecution Of\nMeyer, Petition and Haywood. The\nresolution declares:\n\n\nat is not the intention Of the\ncourts of Idaho to give the accused\nmen fair and Impartial trial. Their\nextradition was contrary to law and\ncovered by fraud, which disgraced\nthe Jurisprudence of the people,\""
    }
